Change History

Revision Date Notes
1.0.1 2016-03-18 Added Debug2 service that supports configuration of setting hostname for the heartbeat server.

Added the following:
  • action GetHeartbeatServer
  • action SetHeartbeatServer

Services

Debug

http://linksys.com/jnap/debug/Debug
This service provides debug access to the router's internal state.

Actions

Echo

http://linksys.com/jnap/debug/Echo
This action echoes input values.

Note:

This action does not require HTTP basic authentication.

Note:

This action is safe to call within the context of a transaction.

Input Parameters

Name Type Optional Description
string string yes A string value.
int int yes An int value.
bool bool yes A bool value.
datetime DateTime yes A datetime value.
ipAddress IPAddress yes An IP address value.
ipv6Address IPv6Address yes An IPv6 address value.
macAddress MACAddress yes A MAC address value.
uuid UUID yes A UUID value.

Output Parameters

Name Type Optional Description
string string yes The string value that was specified in the input, if any.
int int yes The int value that was specified in the input, if any.
bool bool yes The bool value that was specified in the input, if any.
datetime DateTime yes The datetime value that was specified in the input, if any.
ipAddress IPAddress yes The IP address value that was specified in the input, if any.
ipv6Address IPv6Address yes The IPv6 address value that was specified in the input, if any.
macAddress MACAddress yes The MAC address value that was specified in the input, if any.
uuid UUID yes The UUID value that was specified in the input, if any.

Result

http://linksys.com/jnap/debug/EchoResult
Value Description
OK Success.
Error
_ErrorAbortedAction
_ErrorInvalidInput
_ErrorInvalidOutput
_ErrorNotReady
_ErrorSessionVerification
_ErrorUnauthorized
_ErrorUnexpected
_ErrorUnknownAction
_ErrorUnknownSession

Sample Transaction

POST [request-uri] HTTP/1.1
Host: 192.168.1.1
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: [number of octets in request body]
X-JNAP-Action: "http://linksys.com/jnap/debug/Echo"

{
  "string": "example string",
  "int": 123,
  "bool": true,
  "datetime": "2016-07-23T14:30:59Z",
  "ipAddress": "192.168.1.101",
  "ipv6Address": "2001:0DB8:85A3:0000:0000:8A2E:0370:7334",
  "macAddress": "00:22:5F:A1:73:C1",
  "uuid": "c23de4d6-15d0-40bf-8f43-5d354b222992"
}
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: [number of octets in response body]

{
  "result": "OK",
  "output": {
    "string": "example string",
    "int": 123,
    "bool": true,
    "datetime": "2016-07-23T14:30:59Z",
    "ipAddress": "192.168.1.101",
    "ipv6Address": "2001:0DB8:85A3:0000:0000:8A2E:0370:7334",
    "macAddress": "00:22:5F:A1:73:C1",
    "uuid": "c23de4d6-15d0-40bf-8f43-5d354b222992"
  }
}

GetCloudServer

http://linksys.com/jnap/debug/GetCloudServer

Note:

This action does not require HTTP basic authentication.

Note:

This action is safe to call within the context of a transaction.

Input Parameters

This action does not have any input parameters.

Output Parameters

Name Type Optional Description
useSSL bool no Should requests be sent via an SSL tunnel?
host string no The hostname of the server to proxy cloud API calls to.
port int no The port of the server to proxy cloud API calls to.
verify bool no Should the remote server's certificate be verified?

Result

http://linksys.com/jnap/debug/GetCloudServerResult
Value Description
OK Success.
Error
_ErrorAbortedAction
_ErrorInvalidInput
_ErrorInvalidOutput
_ErrorNotReady
_ErrorSessionVerification
_ErrorUnauthorized
_ErrorUnexpected
_ErrorUnknownAction
_ErrorUnknownSession

Sample Transaction

POST [request-uri] HTTP/1.1
Host: 192.168.1.1
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: [number of octets in request body]
X-JNAP-Action: "http://linksys.com/jnap/debug/GetCloudServer"

{
}
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
Content-Length: [number of octets in response body]

{
  "result": "OK",
  "output": {
    "useSSL": true,
    "host": "example string",
    "port": 123,
    "verify": true
  }
}

Structures

Action

http://linksys.com/jnap/debug/Action
Information about a JNAP/HNAP action.

Structure Members

Member Name Type Optional Description
uri string no The action URI.
isJNAP bool no Whether the action is JNAP.
isImplemented bool no Whether the action is implemented by the server.

Module

http://linksys.com/jnap/debug/Module
A JNAP/HNAP server module.

Structure Members

Member Name Type Optional Description
services Service[] no The list of services in the module.
actions Action[] no The list of actions in the module.

Service

http://linksys.com/jnap/debug/Service
Information about a JNAP/HNAP service.

Structure Members

Member Name Type Optional Description
uri string no The service URI.
actionURIs string[] no The list of actions in the service.

SysEntry

http://linksys.com/jnap/debug/SysEntry
This service provides debug access to the router's internal state. This service is only available in non-production firmware builds. A sysconfig or sysevent entry.

Structure Members

Member Name Type Optional Description
name string no The name of the sysconfig or sysevent entry.
value string yes The value of the sysconfig or sysevent entry. This member will not be present if the entry does not exist.
